'''Cafarel''', also known as '''criblez''',<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|III|370|Zeltron}}</ref> were [[Zeltron/Legends|Zeltron]] [[Prostitute/Legends|courtesans]] known for fulfilling any [[Reproduction/Legends|sexual]] desire a being might have, without limits. They were sought out by many [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lords]], especially [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]].<ref name="EGAS">[[The Essential Guide to Alien Species (real-world book)|''The Essential Guide to Alien Species'']]</ref> [[Gender/Legends|Female]] cafarel outnumbered their male counterparts by a factor of twenty to one.<ref name="WIZ">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20040105zeltros|text=Zeltros: Pleasure Planet|int=Zeltros: Pleasure Planet}}</ref> At the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], Zeltron cafarel were often seen sharing [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Miltin Takel]]'s private quarters aboard his personal [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] ''[[Magic Dragon]]''.<ref name="Blog">{{SW|url=news/barely-tolerable-alien-henchmen-of-the-empire-part-2|series=Barely Tolerable: Alien Henchmen of the Empire|text=Part 2|nolive=1}}</ref>

